{"tid":2431211,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[自家烘焙]芝士蒜蓉香草牛油包","createTime":"2021-03-03T12:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T10:04:17.000Z","uid":132749,"like":107,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a45c3696548bf54422eaa54b6103c8cd734b9838","tid":2431211,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:58:02.000Z","msg":"宜排食到無咩好食，係澳洲supermarket 買到既麵包食到就嘔，好難食，又乾又唔香， 就算行過賣d類似香港麵包既包鋪，完全聞唔到香港包鋪陣牛油香味。好掛住香港麵包鋪既麵包，每次行過牛油味好鬼香<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。都唔知幾時先返到去，所以得自己整<br />\n<br />\n今次宜個芝士蒜蓉香草牛油包落左好多牛油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好正， 加埋小小芝士味，真係可以食唔停<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一開始搞左個麵團：<br />\n第一次發酵， 分成6份，鬆20分鍾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L5SQRqz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL5SQRqz.jpg&h=b1d80a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mdAOC5A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmdAOC5A.jpg&h=bab91699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n20分鍾後，搓成長條狀，第二次發酵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HweLFiX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHweLFiX.jpg&h=69dd1f98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L58gMYZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL58gMYZ.jpg&h=3e3ddb4a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yJs5Fi1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyJs5Fi1.jpg&h=b6bfa8f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重點❗️❗️❗️蒜蓉牛油，宜個做法好好食，只有蒜香，又唔會有蒜既辣味， 重點係唔會食到蒜粒，平時好怕食到蒜粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZYiP6XZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZYiP6XZ.jpg&h=8b59ede5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個包發酵好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tx1x4LH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTx1x4LH.jpg&h=e3459d63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多牛油<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z2ai0it.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ2ai0it.jpg&h=efe05fcd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jiCEKLa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjiCEKLa.jpg&h=206d4d10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7PvRqc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7PvRqc.jpg&h=238ecbc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新鮮出爐好鬆軟， 好有香港麵包鋪既味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G7QrpJv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG7QrpJv.jpg&h=dd9a6bd9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LiOMpJy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLiOMpJy.jpg&h=e655f861&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rXZorWW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrXZorWW.jpg&h=a33a747a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LFhmdB0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLFhmdB0.jpg&h=3b21814d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sXypi7vSghw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsXypi7vSghw&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=23bbdc12\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sXypi7vSghw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鍾意既記得subscribe, like 同share 我YouTube Channel,仲有follow 我ig <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYouTube: <a href=\"https://youtube.com/channel/UCGJHwItoXY4IkZX7efJvCXg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCGJHwItoXY4IkZX7efJvCXg&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=6500ff04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/channel/UCGJHwItoXY4IkZX7efJvCXg</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/openfridge_kitchendiary/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fopenfridge_kitchendiary%2F&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=fe5fcfa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/openfridge_kitchendiary/</a>"},{"pid":"604be4c2e3d3c6e12688dc61c6281b68a05e7783","tid":2431211,"uid":35930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:58:59.000Z","msg":"想食到蒜粒嘅應該點做？"},{"pid":"e489a583ed7deb63d95ad02f3d6838482e007bc3","tid":2431211,"uid":261592,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:59:06.000Z","msg":"高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371a7b287b09c68dd90237be79cdfe12f8596d73","tid":2431211,"uid":360231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddff1ef4552a430393941f14d83e971fed3cffb5","tid":2431211,"uid":132749,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"604be4c2e3d3c6e12688dc61c6281b68a05e7783","tid":2431211,"uid":35930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:58:59.000Z","msg":"想食到蒜粒嘅應該點做？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021